{"tid":2094702,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普據報正擬兩至三項應對中國行動　最快數日公布","createTime":"2020-07-05T00:56:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T12:26:30.000Z","uid":18569,"like":376,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":96,"replies":[{"pid":"55b8e6fc8ec6a6c785c53e839552101bb11940f8","tid":2094702,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T00:56:00.000Z","msg":"特朗普據報正擬兩至三項應對中國行動　最快數日公布<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普據報正考慮兩至三項應對中國的行動，預料最快會在數日內公布。美國《彭博》通訊社引述一名華府官員透露有關消息，但未有表明行動涉及的細節，亦未有透露特朗普會否簽署早前由國會參眾兩院一致通過的「香港自治法案」。特朗普又在美國獨立日向民眾發表講話，再次將病毒歸咎於中國，並說美國將戰勝從「中國來的疫情」，將比以往任何時候更加偉大。<br />\n<br />\n2020-07-05 08:50:26<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c351b5282e4adf25a5a41fb31b90bbe536501c33","tid":2094702,"uid":72009,"like":70,"dislike":71,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T00:58:41.000Z","msg":"依2個星期對Trump有少少失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fa65d55a937ef4be06e616c405abe14bab01ab1","tid":2094702,"uid":99962,"like":23,"dislike":29,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T01:00:28.000Z","msg":"買多d大豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff7a43d479dc384b908275e66b25270a4984f267","tid":2094702,"uid":2954,"like":154,"dislike":4,"score":150,"quote":{"pid":"c351b5282e4adf25a5a41fb31b90bbe536501c33","tid":2094702,"uid":72009,"like":70,"dislike":71,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T00:58:41.000Z","msg":"依2個星期對Trump有少少失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T01:00:35.000Z","msg":"大佬佢美國本土d野都未穩定點會理香港住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e70875695acfe5abde3d182f397fe336e2f8e1d0","tid":2094702,"uid":343361,"like":6,"dislike":27,"score":-21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T01:00:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">豆侵</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dr